亦向示威者連開多槍，包括胡椒球彈和布袋彈。<br />\n<br />\n多人吸入催淚氣體不適，亦有記者懷疑被橡膠子彈打中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n羅沃啟認為，相較612金鐘衝突，當晚警方使用武力，仍無改善亦不恰當。他又說，當晚發現有很多警員身上沒有佩戴委任證或警員編號，重申應成立獨立調查委員會調查這些情況。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆指，警務人員在使用武力前會在情況許可下，向對方發出警告，任何人如認為警方處事時受不合理對待，可向投訴警察課投訴。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:07:47.000Z","msg":"回應721官警黑大龍鳳<br />\n727元朗反黑 728上環抗警<br />\n兩線並進 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"8431a2b69cd4128d0cd86b13fcb25f1eec14fae6","tid":1357833,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T21:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b2b533cee4ac3de6bb11d531bfb58c3b8a9f1ba","tid":1357833,"uid":74572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"借位 順手幫推 麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【越洋幫拖】喺美國嘅香港人想收集警暴證據交畀美國警察同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c07e6eed49e114ffc14cc4a780092b800b89752f","tid":1357833,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06d310706d09814bfbe4efb4603ecb65ce2ca1a9","tid":1357833,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"對住別人的後腦開槍<br />\n<br />\n義士下次先要攞制空權"},{"pid":"e0c05f3faa15008157ee7d940e163edac4972a29","tid":1357833,"uid":94340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0773b29f0674072410fcc3f018afe830125bb0","tid":1357833,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma